name: Muth spider
tagline: A hexapod spider robot using Robotis CM-700 controller and Dynamixel servos.
body:
# MuthSpider

A hexapod spider robot controlled by Robotis CM-700 controller and motorized by Robotis Dynamixel AX-18A servos with one sensor Robotis Synamixel AX-S1
